  {
    "type": "EXEGETICAL (ORIGINAL LANGUAGES)",
    "name": "Pulpit Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_sub_title",
        "text": "Verse 25.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "And the promise which he promised us is this,",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " even ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "the eternal life.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greek",
        "text": "Αὐτός",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " is Christ; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greek",
        "text": "αὕτη",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " looks forward to \"the eternal life,\" not backwards to the abiding in the Father (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "John 3:16",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "John 5:24",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "John 6:40, 54",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greek",
        "text": "Τὴν ζωὴν τὴν αἰώνιον",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " is in the accusative by attraction to ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greek",
        "text": "ἥν",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". \"What St. John would have us feel is this, that there can be no promise to compare with this - that we should share the eternal life, the life of God....  We often speak as if people were to be paid for being good; not as if the being good were itself God's highest gift and blessing\" (Maurice). The reading ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greek",
        "text": "ὑμῖν",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (B) for ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greek",
        "text": "ἡμῖν",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " is worthy of notice. In verses 16, 17 St. John gives two reasons for shunning the world: because ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "note_emph",
        "text": "(1)",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " the world is alien to the Father; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "note_emph",
        "text": "(2)",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " it is passing away. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "So here he gives two for holding fast the truth originally delivered to them: because the truth leads ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "note_emph",
        "text": "(1)",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " to fellowship with God; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "note_emph",
        "text": "(2)",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " to eternal life. 1 John 2:25",
        "children": []
